cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.DC 

The paper discusses the problem of video delivery over cognitive radio networks, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), information theory (cs.IT), cognitive radio (cs.CR), and distributed computing (cs.DC). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI, followed by cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.CR, and cs.DC.
